presencevnc (0.8) unstable; urgency=low

  * Add --viewonly, --listen and --help command line options
  * Use less CPU when display is off
  * Improve performance of partial repaints, scrolling more fluent
  * Don't use 32bit color on N900 (16bit display). Greatly reduces transfer
    rate when using high quality.
  * Show more detailed error messages in UI
  * In portrait mode toolbar now only shows zoom slider and fullscreen button

 -- Christian Pulvermacher <pulvermacher@gmx.de>  Sun, 12 Feb 2012 15:49:26 +0100

